WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.623
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.623 --> 00:00:03.720
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.720 --> 00:00:05.040
Glory to God.

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:08.580
Well, it looked like we had some victory when it comes to the hurricane.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:20.105
It went from a Category 5 to a Category 3, and I believe that's by the prayers of the righteous, praying and believing for that thing to fall apart.

00:00:20.330 --> 00:00:21.005
You know what?

00:00:21.005 --> 00:00:23.120
It could have been a lot worse.

00:00:23.120 --> 00:00:32.507
It could have been a lot worse if it would have hit at what it was when it was in the Gulf, but God, who is rich in mercy.

00:00:33.333 --> 00:00:36.177
I just want to say, we're doing it, folks.

00:00:36.177 --> 00:00:37.320
This is why we're here.

00:00:37.320 --> 00:00:43.183
That's why the Lord said, 'Hey, Brandon, I want you to go on and do these prayer videos for the next 30 days.

00:00:43.183 --> 00:00:54.250
' Now, we're going to take communion today again, so if you are new here and you didn't pray with us yesterday or the day before, today's your day, and I'm excited you're here.

00:00:54.250 --> 00:00:59.645
But we have a mission, and it is to disrupt the things of the devil.

00:00:59.645 --> 00:01:11.160
He is not going to have victory in this earth as long as we're here; we have authority over him, and we're going to rise up and take our authority over the devil.

00:01:11.160 --> 00:01:18.189
We don't need to go around hitting the devil in the head like those Whac-A-Mole—you know, those Whac-A-Moles at the fair that are always sticking up.

00:01:18.189 --> 00:01:23.040
I've told everybody this: it's like we're always trying to wait and put out the devil's fires.

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:28.587
The body of Christ is running around with a fire hose, always putting out the devil's fires.

00:01:28.920 --> 00:01:30.440
I said it is ridiculous.

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:32.520
We are watchmen.

00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:39.817
We see far in advance—sometimes I see years, sometimes I see days, sometimes I see even more than five years.

00:01:43.156 --> 00:01:50.655
We'll be up on the wall and we'll see things coming, but we know we're going to put out the fire before he starts it.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:56.160
That's why the Holy Spirit warns us and guides us about all things.

00:01:56.160 --> 00:01:58.467
He doesn't want us to be caught off guard.

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:02.940
Was the hurricane catching us off guard?

00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:03.215
No.

00:02:03.215 --> 00:02:07.680
We know that there are going to be things, but we have authority over them.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:09.528
We know that we're in the end times.

00:02:09.528 --> 00:02:14.680
We know, ladies and gentlemen, that as labor pains come upon a woman, so will it be.

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:19.372
We know it's going to get darker and darker because the Bible told us it would.

00:02:19.372 --> 00:02:20.992
Can we stop it all?

00:02:20.992 --> 00:02:26.720
No, we can't, because some things are going to happen, but we can protect our families.

00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:28.509
You don't have to walk in fear of the devil.

00:02:28.509 --> 00:02:30.415
You don't have to walk in bondage.

00:02:32.185 --> 00:02:40.280
For me and my house, I always say, 'Let the storm rage outside, but there's peace on the inside.

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:45.435
' I am not going to have the devil stir up a storm inside and outside.

00:02:45.435 --> 00:02:49.867
You do what you've got to do; I'm going to take authority over here, and I put a bloodline around my house.

00:02:49.867 --> 00:02:51.400
I take communion daily.

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:56.040
I take my seat and I sit with Him.

00:02:56.234 --> 00:02:57.705
Everybody says, 'Well, you pray too long.

00:02:58.010 --> 00:02:59.535
Your videos go too long.

00:02:59.535 --> 00:03:05.800
' If you're only praying ten minutes a day, you're in trouble because of what I've seen coming.

00:03:05.800 --> 00:03:14.840
People don't want to hear that in the Word of Faith circles because they think you're being negative, but I'm trying to tell you and warn you as a watchman that there's a storm coming.

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:17.704
I'm trying to tell you that we have authority over the storm.

00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:38.480
There are economic things coming and hard days for some people, but we don't have to participate in it.

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:46.013
It's not for us; we're His beloved.

00:03:46.013 --> 00:03:55.840
He will always take care of His beloved.

00:03:55.840 --> 00:04:07.960
He's not up there warning me, 'Oh, Brandon, guess what?

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:13.594
Doom and gloom is coming for you.

00:04:13.594 --> 00:04:20.025
' No, I'm in a covenant with Him.

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:31.152
This is part of my covenant: His body, His blood.

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:48.206
I take it inside of me and I say, 'No, thus far and no further, devil.

00:04:48.206 --> 00:04:55.640
' There are no plagues, no pestilence.

00:04:55.640 --> 00:04:59.456
Psalm 91.

00:04:59.456 --> 00:05:23.800
Just remember what I told you all: I said there was a great storm coming on the East Coast.

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:32.370
Everybody said, 'Well, was that Milton?

00:05:37.514 --> 00:05:37.777
Was that the hurricanes coming?

00:05:37.777 --> 00:05:41.091
' No.

00:05:43.794 --> 00:05:54.975
This was about the Antichrist system, the Antichrist agenda that was trying to come on.

00:05:58.394 --> 00:06:09.690
I could see the bands of the hurricane on the East Coast that was coming from the Gulf.

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:23.105
What I saw was not coming from the Gulf; it was coming from the East Coast.

00:06:24.230 --> 00:06:51.240
It was a massive storm that went all the way from sea to shining sea, from the south all the way to the north.

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:56.010
It was from coast to coast.

00:06:56.010 --> 00:07:09.880
This was a massive storm and the bands started coming upon the land.

00:07:10.823 --> 00:07:17.375
The Lord said to me, 'Remember, I saw a massive Holy Ghost wall.

00:07:17.375 --> 00:07:34.240
' I have to be careful with that word because last time people got mad at me—a massive Holy Ghost barrier.

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:43.133
These people are so liberal and dumb...

00:07:43.133 --> 00:07:58.672
there was a wall of protection for the body of Christ.

00:07:58.672 --> 00:08:14.046
I asked the Lord, and it was thick with humongous bricks.

00:08:22.745 --> 00:08:25.480
It was like four feet thick in each sector.

00:08:30.076 --> 00:08:38.040
On this side was a green valley with a little house that had a chimney.

00:08:38.040 --> 00:08:52.740
Smoke was coming up through the chimney, and there was fresh-baked bread inside of this little fire stove.

00:08:52.740 --> 00:09:14.180
They were cooking this bread, and in the spirit, I could smell the bread that God had prepared for me.

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:29.990
You could see the stream of water that was still and in peace.

00:09:32.333 --> 00:09:49.840
The brook was so clear, it looked like you could just lap it up because it looked like the best water ever.

00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:52.420
Thank God for that.

00:09:52.420 --> 00:10:00.760
There was a table set up perfectly with all these dishes.

00:10:00.760 --> 00:10:15.160
The Lord said to me, 'Brandon, this is Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 combined.

00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:28.471
' I have prepared a table before you in the presence of your enemies.

00:10:28.471 --> 00:10:34.596
He's the Shepherd; we shall not want.

00:10:43.300 --> 00:10:47.994
He makes us lie down in green pastures; He leads us beside the still waters.

00:10:51.870 --> 00:10:53.320
That water was beautiful and perfect.

00:10:54.045 --> 00:11:00.280
You could smell the fresh-baked bread; it was just perfect.

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:08.600
But there was a wall there.

00:11:18.530 --> 00:11:25.817
The name of the Lord is a strong tower, and the righteous run into it and they are safe.

00:11:25.817 --> 00:11:30.760
He's our shield and our buckler.

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:37.320
There was a place of protection there.

00:11:37.320 --> 00:11:49.880
On the other side was a massive storm.

00:11:49.880 --> 00:12:36.016
He says, 'As long as you get Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 deep down in your heart, that storm that's coming won't get on the inside of you.

00:12:36.016 --> 00:13:14.274
' You have got to get Psalm 23 and Psalm 91 deep down inside of your heart, not just by memorization, but so that you can quote it backwards and sideways.

00:13:14.274 --> 00:13:26.320
Meditate on it, renew your mind to Psalm 23 and Psalm 91.

00:13:26.320 --> 00:13:36.389
Get it in you; mutter it like a cow eats cud.

00:13:36.389 --> 00:13:51.093
You know how they spit up the old grass and chew on it again?

00:13:51.093 --> 00:14:01.040
They have all those stomachs to chew on that grass.

00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:15.304
Well, spew the Word of God up out of you and chew it like cud.

00:14:15.304 --> 00:14:25.211
It's an old country term, but it's the truth.

00:14:25.211 --> 00:14:31.280
Get that Word down inside you.

00:14:36.673 --> 00:14:38.433
The Lord said, 'Brandon, you need to increase your scripture reading.

00:14:38.433 --> 00:14:52.840
' He told me that when I'd been going to these meetings with Nancy Dufresne and this healing thing.

00:14:52.840 --> 00:15:12.200
What she was talking about—getting that Word down inside you—went along with what the Holy Spirit told me.

00:15:12.200 --> 00:15:16.490
It was confirmation.

00:15:16.490 --> 00:15:35.095
He said it's time for you to get that Word even deeper down inside of your spirit.

00:15:35.095 --> 00:15:49.449
Faith comes by hearing, and hearing by the Word of God.

00:15:49.449 --> 00:16:04.248
So when the storms come, your house is built on the rock.

00:16:04.248 --> 00:16:24.747
Your house is not built on the sands of life so the storm knocks it down.

00:16:24.747 --> 00:16:40.704
You've got to have your house on a firm foundation.

00:16:40.704 --> 00:16:51.112
Faith works by love, too.

00:16:51.112 --> 00:16:57.645
You've got to get your love walk right.

00:16:57.645 --> 00:17:10.366
You've got to treat people good and walk in love.

00:17:10.366 --> 00:17:19.620
If you say, 'Why is my faith not working?

00:17:19.620 --> 00:17:23.550
' check your love thermostat.

00:17:23.550 --> 00:17:44.010
If you're not treating people right—I'm always quick to repent if I snap at my wife or my kids.

00:17:44.010 --> 00:17:51.560
I instantaneously say, 'Holy Spirit, always be quick to correct me.

00:17:51.560 --> 00:17:57.400
' It's never right to be cranky.

00:17:57.400 --> 00:18:02.484
You've got to walk in love.

00:18:02.702 --> 00:18:17.448
I have learned a lot over the last year walking this channel out by faith.

00:18:17.448 --> 00:18:46.582
The Lord is doing so much, and He keeps telling me, 'Brandon, you've got to spend more time with Me.

00:18:46.582 --> 00:18:56.396
You've got to separate yourself unto Me.

00:18:56.396 --> 00:19:31.275
' I get distracted with doing eBay and Poshmark, and He says, 'Brandon, you've got to take some time and pray more.

00:19:31.275 --> 00:19:36.880
' I'm learning.

00:19:36.880 --> 00:19:42.600
Glory to God.

00:19:42.600 --> 00:19:58.880
I just want to say thank you all for being here.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:07.770
We're going to take communion and we're going to pray.

00:20:07.770 --> 00:20:38.673
I feel the leading of the Holy Spirit to pray today about the people being protected after Milton, but we've also got to pray over the election.

00:20:47.753 --> 00:20:53.823
The Lord said for the next 30 days to pray over the election.

00:20:53.823 --> 00:21:05.740
I saw a week's span of time bolded: Wednesday, Thursday, Friday.

00:21:20.225 --> 00:21:21.285
I saw a secret plan where all hidden things will be revealed.

00:21:28.200 --> 00:21:29.355
I saw trucks with mail-in stuff and corruption.

00:21:29.355 --> 00:21:59.404
But this was cool: I saw such a windfall—a voice of expression saying, 'This is the way we want our country to go.

00:21:59.404 --> 00:22:26.445
' It was so overwhelming they did not know what to do because they didn't realize how much of a windfall it would be.

00:22:29.709 --> 00:22:36.380
It was about the Senate and the House.

00:22:36.380 --> 00:22:50.880
Having all three—the House, Senate, and presidency—makes sense because you can change things quickly.

00:23:01.250 --> 00:23:20.775
You can turn the government around, whereas things can be deadlocked if you only have the House and the presidency.

00:23:28.840 --> 00:23:29.433
We have got to stop the enemy.

00:23:29.433 --> 00:23:44.679
There are going to be things that change quickly.

00:23:44.679 --> 00:23:59.143
I told you about the dam that was massive with all that sludge.

00:23:59.143 --> 00:24:33.495
They were going to wait until after the election to release that dam full of the 'swamp'—the nasty sludge of the financial crisis and the dollar crash.

00:24:33.495 --> 00:24:50.405
They were trying to hold it back, but that dam had stress cracks all over it.

00:24:53.940 --> 00:24:54.780
The housing market was shaking.

00:24:54.780 --> 00:25:12.120
Jerome Powell's face was sweating and the housing market was on the bubble.

00:25:12.120 --> 00:25:20.155
From what I understand, that's happening right now.

00:25:20.155 --> 00:25:35.055
I'm not a real estate expert, but from what I hear, that stuff is happening.

00:25:35.055 --> 00:25:52.640
We have authority, so we're going to take communion first.

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:55.689
I don't want to ramble.

00:26:02.498 --> 00:26:08.040
Father, I just thank You for Your body and Your blood.

00:26:09.000 --> 00:26:27.820
I take this every day as a representation of what You did for me.

00:26:29.380 --> 00:26:53.920
I thank You that it is the meal that heals, and that by His stripes, I am healed.

00:26:53.920 --> 00:27:13.440
No COVIDs, no flus, no viruses of any kind, no cancers, no pestilence, no plagues, no tumors.

00:27:18.315 --> 00:27:19.725
I walk in divine health.

00:27:19.725 --> 00:27:31.047
As I take this body, I am wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

00:27:31.047 --> 00:27:53.620
Every cell in my body is in You and You in me.

00:27:53.620 --> 00:28:04.600
There is nothing missing and nothing broken.

00:28:13.300 --> 00:28:13.650
I have shalom.

00:28:13.650 --> 00:28:43.653
Now, Lord, we take this blood and we apply the blood of Jesus over our sins and over our families.

00:28:43.653 --> 00:28:47.674
No calamity is coming near us.

00:28:49.729 --> 00:28:52.480
I plead the blood.

00:28:52.480 --> 00:29:06.600
Satan, no weapon formed against us is going to prosper.

00:29:06.600 --> 00:29:12.830
We can eat or drink any deadly thing and it will not harm us.

00:29:16.431 --> 00:29:31.995
I have a renewed mind and I plead the blood over my mind and emotions.

00:29:31.995 --> 00:29:39.256
I have a sound mind according to 2 Timothy 1:7.

00:29:39.256 --> 00:29:53.520
I thank You that the eyes of my understanding are enlightened.

00:29:53.520 --> 00:30:01.615
Your blood gives us access to that mercy seat.

00:30:01.615 --> 00:30:03.271
Father, we thank You.

00:30:03.271 --> 00:30:09.693
Your mercy is new every morning.

00:30:09.693 --> 00:30:13.720
We pray over the elections.

00:30:20.100 --> 00:30:25.800
In the name of Jesus, Satan, get your hands off of our election.

00:30:25.800 --> 00:30:33.530
This will be a free election without corruption.

00:30:33.530 --> 00:30:48.540
I thank You, Father, that Your angelic beings are going right now to the polling stations.

00:30:48.540 --> 00:30:55.250
Your angels are uncovering all the darkness supernaturally.

00:30:55.585 --> 00:31:08.536
We thank You for supernatural protection concerning our land and our election.

00:31:08.536 --> 00:31:19.389
We call the House and the Senate into righteousness.

00:31:19.389 --> 00:31:31.040
We call for a red wave of Your glory over this land.

00:31:31.600 --> 00:31:39.074
The righteous and even the heathen will get out and vote red.

00:31:39.074 --> 00:31:48.937
They will say, 'Enough is enough' with the border drama and the thievery.

00:31:48.937 --> 00:31:55.880
We're not going to allow America to fall apart.

00:31:55.880 --> 00:32:04.955
Father, I thank You that You raise up godly men and women in leadership.

00:32:04.955 --> 00:32:09.440
We call forth an awakening unto You.

00:32:09.440 --> 00:32:17.080
We call forth a manifestation of a waterfall of turnaround.

00:32:17.080 --> 00:32:27.806
What the devil meant for bad, You will turn for good.

00:32:27.806 --> 00:32:51.080
I thank You that there's going to be a great revival with Brush Arbor churches and big stadiums full of people worshiping Jesus like they did in the Billy Graham meetings.

00:32:51.080 --> 00:32:54.840
This land is not done yet.

00:32:54.840 --> 00:33:00.670
You said America will remain a sheep nation.

00:33:00.670 --> 00:33:07.154
You will not have your way here, devil.

00:33:07.154 --> 00:33:19.113
We are the salt and we hold the blood of Jesus against you.

00:33:19.113 --> 00:33:38.520
Father, stir in the hearts of the ministers and the pastors to stop preaching compromise and a lukewarm gospel—the seeker-friendly message.

00:33:38.520 --> 00:33:47.989
I thank You, Lord, that there will be a great harvest of souls.

00:33:47.989 --> 00:34:00.103
America will be saved, Asia will be saved, Africa, Europe, the Middle East, South America, and Australia.

00:34:00.103 --> 00:34:06.554
We call the blinders off of people's eyes.

00:34:06.554 --> 00:34:16.760
I thank You, Father, for Your grace and mercy.

00:34:16.760 --> 00:34:23.229
Give us one last push for revival.

00:34:23.229 --> 00:34:36.314
We need a revelation of what we have, to walk in Your manifested presence.

00:34:36.314 --> 00:34:50.640
I thank You, Lord, for the Shekinah glory like You did with William Seymour at Azusa.

00:34:50.640 --> 00:34:54.120
Please do it again.

00:34:54.120 --> 00:35:01.680
It has to do with humility.

00:35:01.680 --> 00:35:14.990
I thank You, Lord, that this would be the harvest of all harvests.

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:28.937
Those trucks I saw with all those mail-in ballots—I call for an exposing of corruption.

00:35:28.937 --> 00:35:32.300
Expose, expose, expose!

00:35:32.300 --> 00:35:55.840
We take authority over civil war in this nation; we will not have brother against brother.

00:35:55.840 --> 00:36:08.463
This will be a place of revival and peace.

00:36:08.463 --> 00:36:30.600
There will not be a draft or a call to arms; it will be a call to peace and joy.

00:36:30.600 --> 00:37:12.472
I saw that massive snake come up out of the Gulf of Mexico and wrap around this nation, and You said, 'Who will stand in the gap for America?

00:37:12.472 --> 00:37:20.574
' We say, 'Yes, Lord, we will intercede.

00:37:20.574 --> 00:37:34.880
' What the devil meant for bad, You are going to turn for good.

00:37:34.880 --> 00:37:38.490
I believe I receive.

00:37:38.490 --> 00:38:05.512
Holy Spirit, I ask You right now to pray through us.

00:38:05.512 --> 00:39:26.224
I'm going to pray over healing for your bodies and against terrorist attacks during the elections, or at baseball games, or at Coachella this weekend with President Trump.

00:39:26.224 --> 00:39:43.430
We're going to pray in the spirit to get some direction.

00:39:43.440 --> 00:40:11.298
If you haven't prayed in a new tongue, just listen along.

00:40:11.298 --> 00:41:33.250
You've got to pray it out by faith.

00:41:33.250 --> 00:41:51.638
Father, we yield to You.

00:41:51.638 --> 00:42:17.150
Everything that's hidden be revealed.

00:42:17.150 --> 00:43:01.350
Do you want to go to the mountain of the Lord?

00:43:01.360 --> 00:44:29.640
For there is a place for those who are thirsty in the mountain of the Lord.

00:44:29.640 --> 00:44:41.907
Lord, we need You more.

00:44:41.907 --> 00:45:22.400
Then sings my soul, my Savior God, to Thee, how great Thou art.

00:45:40.600 --> 00:45:51.593
He walked the streets of Calvary, the rugged cross He bore.

00:46:36.359 --> 00:46:51.947
When He was on the cross, I was on His mind.

00:46:55.320 --> 00:47:07.415
He knew me, but yet He loved me.

00:47:42.200 --> 00:47:48.550
We were on His mind.

00:47:48.560 --> 00:48:50.730
Oh, the glory of Your presence.

00:50:08.280 --> 00:50:20.800
Arise from Your rest and be blessed by our praise.

00:50:44.360 --> 00:51:03.200
We need Your help, Holy Spirit, to flow, digging out the old wells of revival like Isaac dug the wells that his father once dug.

00:51:07.760 --> 00:51:18.230
We get the new wells for something new.

00:51:33.720 --> 00:51:39.200
We ain't going back to the past; we're going forward.

00:52:26.180 --> 00:52:56.150
Lord, we worship You.

00:52:56.160 --> 00:53:46.700
You alone are holy; You alone are worthy.

00:53:46.700 --> 00:54:08.180
When I pray in the spirit, don't let your faith be disengaged.

00:54:08.180 --> 00:54:18.935
Focus on Him.

00:54:18.935 --> 00:54:53.070
Don't let your mouth go on autopilot while you think about what you have to do later.

00:54:53.070 --> 00:54:58.476
Focus on His face.

00:54:58.476 --> 00:55:23.720
Engage your spirit toward Him and say, 'Lord, show me the things to come.

00:55:23.720 --> 00:56:08.200
' Focus your faith on the target—the elections, protection for Donald Trump, your finances, or healing for your body.

00:56:08.200 --> 00:57:34.680
Father, we thank You for this prayer time and the mysteries we prayed out.

00:57:34.680 --> 00:57:42.987
We expect results and a supernatural turnaround.

00:57:42.987 --> 00:57:44.720
I'm going to keep praying.

00:57:44.720 --> 00:58:03.175
My wife wants to share a book we've been reading by John Bevere that is absolutely life-changing.

00:58:03.175 --> 00:58:13.027
She also wants to talk about these tower gardens.

00:58:13.027 --> 00:58:32.497
A sister in the Lord blessed us with these, and they are a great way to have replenishable food.

00:58:32.497 --> 00:58:41.611
I've been praying about health and preparing with wisdom.

00:58:41.611 --> 00:58:52.109
These gardens grow lettuce and tomatoes inside your house with lights.

00:58:52.109 --> 00:58:57.853
If the electric grid went down, you could use a solar box to keep it going.

00:59:07.820 --> 00:59:10.400
It's a way to have fresh vegetables without needing tons of canned food.

00:59:10.971 --> 00:59:21.667
I had chickens for a while, but they were messy and ate all the grass.

00:59:21.667 --> 00:59:35.549
These gardens are a creative idea for the times ahead.

00:59:35.549 --> 00:59:47.480
If this is your first time here, please like our videos.

00:59:52.488 --> 01:00:01.807
It helps us with the algorithm and gets the videos promoted.

01:00:01.807 --> 01:00:10.897
Comment down below and tell us where you're from.

01:00:10.897 --> 01:00:32.584
People ask why I wear this prayer shawl; I do it for me as a covering.

01:00:32.584 --> 01:00:42.710
Jesus loves you so much.

01:00:45.240 --> 01:00:58.680
We will see you again tomorrow and every day until the election.

01:00:58.680 --> 01:01:05.740
Be blessed and have an amazing day.

01:01:05.740 --> 01:01:11.480
God bless you all.

01:01:11.480 --> 01:01:12.737
Bye-bye.
